flowchart TD
    U[Users / Tools / Agents / CI-CD / Automation] --> E[Microsoft Entra ID]
    E --> APIM[Azure API Management optional]
    APIM --> G[Gateway Service - Container Apps]

    G --> RC{Redis cache hit?}
    RC -->|Yes| R[Return scoped context bundle]
    RC -->|No| IDX[Index / Standards Services]

    IDX --> CDB[Cosmos DB Vector Search + Metadata + Source Pointers]
    CDB --> CONN[Connector Layer]

    CONN --> GH[GitHub]
    CONN --> ADO[Azure DevOps]
    CONN --> CONF[Confluence]
    CONN --> SP[SharePoint]

    GH --> SRC[Authoritative source content]
    ADO --> SRC
    CONF --> SRC
    SP --> SRC

    SRC --> BLOB[Blob Storage cache/artifacts]
    BLOB --> ASM[Bundle Assembly + Governance]
    ASM --> REDIS[Redis Semantic Cache]
    REDIS --> R

    SB[Azure Service Bus] --> WK[Worker Services]
    WK --> CDB
    WK --> BLOB
    WK --> REDIS
    WK --> CONN